headline: Gilead, Terray Therapeutics announce research collaboration
summary: Gilead (GILD) and Terray Therapeutics announced that the companies have entered into a strategic collaboration to discover and develop novel, small molecule therapies across multiple targets. Terray’s tNova platform combines high-throughput chemical experimentation and computational analysis with a generative AI-driven drug discovery engine.
